task.summary: 1.the tag has been made. 2.the renderer has been controlled in unused time. 3.the key track UI has been made. 4.the object control panel has been made and control its position until now. 5.the UI has been optimized for all devices just according to percentages. 6.the Vue has been removed from all the Project. it is very less useful product for us. 7.the initial position of the camera has been optimized. 8.an event listener has been added to listen any action of the orbitControls. 9.the geometryElements.js has been optimized. 10.make it possible to add the X,Y,Z label on the Axis by using the Sprite. 11.optimized the CreateGeometry function ,removeObject function and activateTargetMesh function . 12.new add the setCurrObject function in order to show the some information of the current active mesh object on the UI .
